cute;daction (en)</a> lorsqu&rsquo;un autre r&eacute;dacteur est d&eacute;j&agrave; sur l&rsquo;article en cours. Une fen&ecirc;tre apparaitra pour signaler cela.</p>\n<p>On parle aussi de l&rsquo;avenir de l&rsquo;<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wprealm.com/blog/admin-panel-what-does-the-future-hold/">interface d&rsquo;administration (en)</a>.</p>\n<h3>GlotPress revient</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://blog.glotpress.org/2013/03/08/a-few-hours-ago-we-had-our-first/">Les discussions (en) </a>autour du projet de traduction GlotPress sont de retour.</p>\n<h3>Cacher le nom d&rsquo;admin</h3>\n<p>C&rsquo;est maintenant possible de cacher le nom d&rsquo;admin afin de s&eacute;curiser davantage votre installation. <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/user-name-security/">Ceci gr&acirc;ce &agrave; l&rsquo;extension de Daniel Roch (en)</a>.</p>\n<h3>D&eacute;busquer les th&egrave;mes crypt&eacute;s</h3>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.apprentiphotographe.ch/debusquez-les-themes-wordpress-cryptes/">Une m&eacute;thode simple et pratique </a>pour d&eacute;busquer les th&egrave;mes crypt&eacute;s qui passe par l&rsquo;installation d&rsquo;une extension.</p>\n<p>WordPress en mode &laquo;&nbsp;debug&nbsp;&raquo;</p>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://tweetpress.fr/screencast/debug-wordpress/">Comment utiliser WordPress en mode d&eacute;bogage</a>, Julien nous explique tout.</p>\n<h3>R&eacute;tablir le javascript dans l&rsquo;admin</h3>\n<p>Si le javascript a disparu de votre admin, <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wpchannel.com/corriger-bug-aucun-javascript-administration-wordpress/">voici la solution</a>.</p>\n<h3>Wysija : la newsletter facile</h3>\n<p>Wysija est une extension permettant la gestion de newsletter. <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wpformation.com/wysija-newsletter-plugin-wordpress/">Pr&eacute;sentation par Fabrice Ducarme</a>.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=81ngebJIp0c:h3Fma4JnQqY:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=81ngebJIp0c:h3Fma4JnQqY:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=81ngebJIp0c:h3Fma4JnQqY:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=81ngebJIp0c:h3Fma4JnQqY:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?a=81ngebJIp0c:h3Fma4JnQqY:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/WordpressFrancophone?i=81ngebJIp0c:h3Fma4JnQqY:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></a>\n</div>\n<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/WordpressFrancophone/~4/81ngebJIp0c" height="1" width="1">\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:59:"Here With Me : Ce à quoi pourrait ressembler WordPress 3.6";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:80:"http://www.herewithme.fr/2013/03/09/ce-a-quoi-pourrait-ressembler-wordpress-3-6/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:80:"http://www.herewithme.fr/2013/03/09/ce-a-quoi-pourrait-ressembler-wordpress-3-6/";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2013-03-09T20:52:56+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:6:"author";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"name";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"anonymous";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}s:7:"content";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3922:"<div>\n<p>&Ccedil;a&nbsp;travaille dur dans la communaut&eacute; pour am&eacute;liorer encore et toujours notre CMS pr&eacute;f&eacute;r&eacute; ! J&rsquo;ai &eacute;voqu&eacute; les nouveaut&eacute;s de la version 3.6 dans un <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.herewithme.fr/2013/01/08/premieres-orientations-pour-wordpress-3-6/">pr&eacute;c&eacute;dent billet</a>, mais depuis certaines fonctionnalit&eacute;s ont &eacute;t&eacute; report&eacute;es (workflow de publication), et d&rsquo;autres modifications ont &eacute;t&eacute; annonc&eacute;es.</p>\n<p>C&rsquo;est notamment le cas de l&rsquo;apparence de WordPress, aussi bien cot&eacute; public avec un nouveau th&egrave;me &laquo;&nbsp;Twenty Thirteen&nbsp;&raquo; que la console d&rsquo;administration avec peut-&ecirc;tre un restylage.</p>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://make.wordpress.org/core/2013/02/18/introducing-twenty-thirteen/">Twenty Thirteen</a> est un th&egrave;me orient&eacute; blog, avec l&rsquo;accent mis sur les posts formats.</p>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.herewithme.fr/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/About-Twenty-Thirteen-e1362858220244.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1335" alt="About Twenty Thirteen e1362858220244 300x207 Ce &agrave; quoi pourrait ressembler WordPress 3.6" src="http://www.herewithme.fr/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/About-Twenty-Thirteen-e1362858220244-300x207.png" width="300" height="207" title="Ce &agrave; quoi pourrait ressembler WordPress 3.6"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Concernant la console d&rsquo;administration, un projet d&rsquo;&eacute;volution est disponible sous la forme d&rsquo;une extension nomm&eacute;e&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/mp6/">MP6</a>.&nbsp;&Agrave;&nbsp;ce stade, rien ne garantit que cette &eacute;volution de l&rsquo;interface soit int&eacute;gr&eacute;e dans le projet, c&rsquo;est une extension &laquo;&nbsp;laboratoire&nbsp;&raquo;. Tous les d&eacute;tails sur le blog <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://make.wordpress.org/ui/2013/03/09/as-a-continuation-of-the-work-begun-in/">make UI</a>.</p>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.herewithme.fr/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Tableau-de-bord-%E2%80%B9-Test-de-plugins-%E2%80%94-WordPress.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1338" alt="Tableau de bord &lsaquo; Test de plugins &mdash; WordPress 274x300 Ce &agrave; quoi pourrait ressembler WordPress 3.6" src="http://www.herewithme.fr/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Tableau-de-bord-%E2%80%B9-Test-de-plugins-%E2%80%94-WordPress-274x300.png" width="274" height="300" title="Ce &agrave; quoi pourrait ressembler WordPress 3.6"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.herewithme.fr/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Modifier-l%E2%80%99article-%E2%80%B9-Test-de-plugins-%E2%80%94-WordPress.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1337" alt="Modifier l&rsquo;article &lsaquo; Test de plugins &mdash; WordPress 182x300 Ce &agrave; quoi pourrait ressembler WordPress 3.6" src="http://www.herewithme.fr/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Modifier-l%E2%80%99article-%E2%80%B9-Test-de-plugins-%E2%80%94-WordPress-182x300.png" width="182" height="300" title="Ce &agrave; quoi pourrait ressembler WordPress 3.6"></a> <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://www.herewithme.fr/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/R%C3%A9glages-des-m%C3%A9dias-%E2%80%B9-Test-de-plugins-%E2%80%94-WordPress.png"><img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1336" alt="R&eacute;glages des m&eacute;dias &lsaquo; Test de plugins &mdash; WordPress 300x241 Ce &agrave; quoi pourrait ressembler WordPress 3.6" src="http://www.herewithme.fr/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/R%C3%A9glages-des-m%C3%A9dias-%E2%80%B9-Test-de-plugins-%E2%80%94-WordPress-300x241.png" width="300" height="241" title="Ce &agrave; quoi pourrait ressembler WordPress 3.6"></a></p>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:39:"4h18 : Une session spéciale BuddyPress";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:131:"http://4h18.com/une-session-speciale-buddypress/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=une-session-speciale-buddypress";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"rel";s:9:"alternate";s:4:"href";s:131:"http://4h18.com/une-session-speciale-buddypress/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=une-session-speciale-buddypress";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:9:"published";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"2013-03-06T09:41:26+00:00";s:7:"attribs";a:0